	},
	{
		heading: "Restaurants, Coffee Shops & Boutique Retail",
		description: "Drive foot traffic and online discovery for Liberty Station restaurants, Shelter Island dining, and boutique shops. We target both locals and tourists searching for Point Loma experiences."
	},
	{
		heading: "Real Estate Agents & Property Management Firms",
		description: "Dominate local real estate searches in Point Loma, Ocean Beach, and coastal neighborhoods. We optimize for buyer, seller, and rental searches that generate qualified leads."
	},
	{
		heading: "Med Spas, Wellness Centers & Salons",
		description: "Stand out in Point Loma's competitive wellness market. We target high-intent searches like \"med spa Point Loma,\" \"massage near Liberty Station,\" and wellness services that attract loyal clients."
	},
	{
